{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/Logo_Evergreen_Texto.png?t=1729061933\" /><br><br><i>Evergreen is a simulation game about leaving the stress of the city behind and starting a new life in a mountain valley.</i><br><br>This simulation game is meant to be a relaxing and calming experience. Forget about stressful hunger, health or temperature meters. Build your house with your own hands, collect the resources that nature provides, travel to a small village to sell what you don't need, buy supplies in stores and admire the wonders of nature.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/T\u00edtulo_Pr\u00f3logo.png?t=1729061933\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In the Evergreen prologue, you will be able to experience your first day in the valley. <br></li><li>The map size is limited, but the main mechanics are all there and polished. <br></li><li>Chop down trees, mine stone and start building your new home in this beautiful world. <br></li><li>Take your car and travel to a nearby town to buy some supplies or furniture to decorate your place.</li></ul><br>Don't forget to add the full game to your wishlist and visit the store page to see what is included in the complete game!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/Separador.png?t=1729061933\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/Gif_Construcciones.gif?t=1729061933\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/Gif_Ciervo.gif?t=1729061933\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/Gif_Coche.gif?t=1729061933\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"http